<p local-id=3D"400bc13b2732">1.3 Comparison =E2=80=94 Classic OAuth 2.0 vs =
RAR</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"c100def82319">
<p local-id=3D"c50c633b6157">Part 2 =E2=80=94 OAuth 2.0 + RAR without PAR</=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"b954cb874e32">
<li local-id=3D"8b30bd565005">
<p local-id=3D"596c0964fff1">2.1 The Problem =E2=80=94 RAR Solves Semantics=
 but Not Transport</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b9d84cc18e4d">
<p local-id=3D"dee810656943">2.2 Attack Surface =E2=80=94 Where the Data Le=
aks</p></li>
