<p local-id=3D"2b4ac10f6eb6">2.3 The Solution =E2=80=94 Pushed Authorizatio=
n Requests (RFC 9126)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"73e979d8e89b">
<p local-id=3D"baefb577b72a">2.4 Why RAR and PAR Must Be Used Together</p><=
/li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"d25610a4c205">
<p local-id=3D"1b57159dca95">Part 3 =E2=80=94 Fine-Grained Authorization wi=
th a Policy Decision Point (PDP)</p>
