<p local-id=3D"146dbb6883ca">3.4 What the PDP Evaluates =E2=80=94 Policy Ca=
tegories</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"74cd1059b9f3">
<p local-id=3D"99fe9b7ec6dc">3.5 PDP Engines =E2=80=94 Available Implementa=
